    "This skill is valuable not just in interacting with AI but in formulating research questions in general.",
    "Working with GenAI allows students to appreciate the strengths and weaknesses of AI technologies, fostering a realistic understanding of what AI can and cannot do.",
    "We hope to continue with this research and advance our understanding of prompt engineering in the sciences which is critical in deploying this powerful technology in the classroom.",
    "This type of training also helps prepare students for their future career paths in STEM, humanities, and social sciences.In conclusion, while GenAI holds significant promise for transforming education, realizing its full potential requires a deeper understanding of its capabilities and limitations.",
    "Our current findings point to the need for targeted improvements in GenAI's ability to generate depth and make inferences."
